#: ../../../app/views/pages/generate_key.html.erb:75
msgid ""
"A default key is used if none is provided. This works but is less secure than "
"a custom key."
msgstr ""
"Sjálfgefinn lykill er notaður ef enginn er gefinn upp. Þetta virkar en er óöru"
"ggara en sérsniðinn lykill."

#: ../../../app/views/pages/generate_key.html.erb:85
msgid "Reduce Risk"
msgstr "Minnka áhættu"

#: ../../../app/views/pages/generate_key.html.erb:88
msgid ""
"Using short push expirations (e.g., 1 day/1 view) reduces risk even with the d"
"efault key."
msgstr ""
"Notkun stuttra gildistíma fyrir tilkynningar (t.d. 1 dagur/1 skoðun) dregur úr"
" áhættu, jafnvel með sjálfgefnum lykli."

